                </div>
                <span data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#demo">
                    <img src="~/newassets/images/info_icon.png" style="cursor:pointer; margin-top: -20px " />
                </span>
                <div id="demo" class="collapse" style="border: 1px solid rgb(143, 213, 0); background:white; padding: 4px; width: 360px;top:155px;z-index:1000;position: absolute; left:383px;">
                    <ul style="margin:0 0 0 20px;">
                        <li>Statute of limitations outlines the timeframes within which legal proceedings must be brought.</li>
                        <li>Search here for the period of limitation prescribed under various acts, matters, suits etc. Type the search term and select from the list.</li>
                        <li>Add the start date calculated manually basis your matter on hand and click +.</li>
